item.title: CVE-2023-44296|2024-08-29T14:51:19.648Z -- dell -- mobility%20-%20e-lab%20navigator
item.description: Dell ELab-Navigator, version 3.1.9 contains a hard-coded credential vulnerability. A local attacker could potentially exploit this vulnerability, leading to unauthorized access to sensitive data. Successful exploitation may result in the compromise of confidential user information.
